        "action": "Implement a policy against gender-based pricing, or \"Pink Tax\"",
        "additional_details": "In an Early Day Motion in 2020, MPs noted that products marketed at women are, in some cases, \u201c34 per cent more expensive than those aimed at men\u201d.",
